(52, 'THROW PILLOWS', '', 'Beautiful designed pillows with soft stuffs, comfortably use for kids in sleeping time, they feature amazing print like text print, cartoon print, art print on Printed pillows in Delhi, select our printed pillows, which is printed with famous artist and designer.'),
(53, 'NOTEBOOKS', '', 'Perfectly-sized notebooks with spiral binding and blank pages that cater to all your writing, journalism or doodling needs. The cover is placed with the artwork you select, neatly printed onto it printed notebooks in Delhi. Get yours today and let the creativity flow!'),
(54, 'TOTE BAGS', '', 'Shop for amazing tote bags – they are light, trendy and feature incredible artwork from illustrators around the world. They come with comfortable straps and high quality printing on both sides order online printed Tote Bags in Delhi. Get yours today!'),
(55, 'MUGS', '', 'Beautiful ceramic mug pieces that needs to be on every coffee table, they feature amazing artwork curated personally by us that is printed across the surface. So now, enjoy your coffee in a mug that truly expresses you!'),
